What is Food Synergism?

Food synergism is the idea that the interaction between certain food compounds enhances their health benefits.

Pairing the right ingredients can boost nutrient absorption, improve digestion, and support immunity.

Tomatoes + Olive Oil

Boosts lycopene absorption with healthy fats.

Spinach + Lemon Juice

Vitamin C increases iron uptake.

Turmeric + Black Pepper

Piperine enhances curcumin bioavailability by 2000%.

Garlic + Honey

Combines antimicrobial and antioxidant power.
